Project

Compass One is an open-source financial guidance platform designed to help individuals make informed financial decisions through transparent, responsible, and secure technology.

The platform is powered by Systrix (System Intelligence Matrix), a modular intelligence engine designed around AI provider independence, extensibility, security, and long-term maintainability.

